      <div class="msgContentFrame">Seems like a Japanese Carpenter (Alive Fox) has made the lance <br />Looking for ideas on what the recipe could be. <br /> <br />I have tried: <br /> <br /><b>What I know to be 100%</b> <br />Iron Lance Blade <br />Iron Lance Butt <br />Cedar Spear Shaft <br /> <br /><b>What I am assuming is right</b> <br />Iron Spear Clasp (could possibly not require a clasp?) <br /> <br /> <br /><b>I have tried (all failed)</b> <br />Iron Lance Blade <br />Iron Lance Butt <br />Cedar Spear Shaft <br />Iron Spear Clasp <br />Wing Glue <br />-------- <br />Iron Lance Blade <br />Iron Lance Butt <br />Cedar Spear Shaft <br />Iron Spear Clasp <br />Horn Glue <br />-------- <br />Iron Lance Blade <br />Iron Lance Butt <br />Cedar Spear Shaft <br />Iron Spear Clasp <br />Iron Rivets (possibly riveted on?) <br />-------- <br />Iron Lance Blade <br />Iron Lance Butt <br />Cedar Spear Shaft <br />Iron Spear Clasp <br />Wing/Horn Glue <br />+ Nuggets/squares (Metal rings around grip on spear possible more iron in synth?) <br /> <br />Any input might help. <br /> <br />[IMG]<a href="http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v324/SilverBlade830/1C60001E.png" title="http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v324/SilverBlade830/1C60001E.png" rel="external nofollow">http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v324/SilverBlade830/1C60001E.png</a>[/IMG] <br />[IMG]<a href="http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v324/SilverBlade830/lance.png" title="http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v324/SilverBlade830/lance.png" rel="external nofollow">http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v324/SilverBlade830/lance.png</a>[/IMG] <br /> <br /> <br /><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>Albel Nox <br />Saronia <br />Top Lancer <br /> <br />Dreadnoughtls.com</div></div>
